	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The CopyNES just plugs directly into where the CPU was, so it should be able to work fine whether it's a Famicom or NES board. It's not designed to fit in the Famicom case, obviously, but it's be really hard to fit much of anything in there.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
